e the complete story script with dialogue for each scene. Keep each scene to 2-3 sentences. Include emotional moments and a satisfying conclusion.\"\t12-scene script\tFlows well, proper length Step 2: Visual Creation with Midjourney/DALL-E Step\tAction\tPrompt Formula\tSettings\tSuccess Criteria 2.1\tCharacter Reference\t\"Create a character sheet for [NAME], a [AGE] year old [DESCRIPTION], children's book illustration style, consistent lighting, white background --ar 1:1 --style raw\"\tHigh quality, seed number\tCharacter consistency 2.2\tScene Illustrations\t\"Scene [NUMBER]: [CHARACTER NAME] [ACTION] in [SETTING], children's book illustration, bright colors, magical atmosphere, same character from reference --ar 4:3 --seed [NUMBER]\"\tSame seed/style\tVisual continuity 2.3\tCover Design\t\"[CHARACTER] on magical Christmas adventure, book cover style, title space at top, professional children's book cover --ar 2:3\"\tBook cover specs\tMarketable design Step 3: Shopify Store Setup (No-Code) Phase\tTask\tSpecific Instructions\tExpected Result\tTime Investment Foundation\tDomain & Theme\t1. Buy domain: [yourname]stories.com 2. Choose theme: \"Craft\" or \"Brooklyn\" 3. Customize colors: warm, child-friendly\tProfessional store\t30 min Products\tBook Listings\t1. Create product variants (ages 3-5, 6-8, 9-12) 2. Add personalization options 3. Set inventory to \"unlimited\" (POD)\tLive products\t45 min Checkout\tPayment & Shipping\t1. Enable Shopify Payments 2. Set shipping rates: $4.99 standard, $12.99 express 3. Add customer info collection\tFunctional purchase flow\t20 min Apps\tEssential Integrations\t1. Loox (reviews) 2. Printful (fulfillment) 3. PostHog (analytics) 4. Facebook Pixel\tAutomated operations\t60 min 🎯 MARKETING & CUSTOMER ACQUISITION Facebook Ads Strategy (6-Figure Monthly Spend Model) Campaign Type\tDaily Budget\tTarget Audience\tCreative Type\tExpected ROAS\tScaling Timeline Testing\t$50/day\tParents 25-45, household income >$50K\tCarousel + video\t